<h2 class="accord">HOW WE SHARE INFORMATION WITH OTHERS</h2>
<div><span> 
<ul>
<li>We work closely with a number of trusted partners with whom we need to share information to help us provide our services: our subsidiaries: <ol>
<li>
<p>Air SERBIA GROUND SERVICES BEOGRAD, seated in Republic of Serbia, Aerodrom Nikola Tesla Beograd,</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>AIR SERBIA CATERING BEOGRAD, in Republic of Serbia, Aerodrom Nikola Tesla Beograd and our outstations</p>
</li>
</ol> </li>
<li>Partner airlines where you are traveling on a booking which involves a codeshare;</li>
<li>Frequent flyer and other reward and partner programs where required to enable you to earn or utilize frequent flyer miles by virtue of your membership of Etihad Guest;</li>
<li>Banks and payment providers, to authorize and complete payments;</li>
<li>Other third parties who help manage our business and deliver services.  For example, these may include IT service providers who help manage our IT and back office systems, or third party booking agents;</li>
<li>With customs and / or immigration departments or other regulatory authorities or government entities, to comply with legal obligations and ensure the safety of all our passengers and customers; and</li>
</ul>
<p>From time to time we may share information about you with government organizations and agencies, and international organizations, to comply with applicable laws, regulations and rules, and legitimate requests from law enforcement, regulatory and other governmental or international agencies, or when to do so is in our legitimate interests, even if we are not compelled to share that information by applicable law.  Further information about when we do this can be found above.</p>
<p>If, in the future, we sell or transfer some or all of our business or assets to a third party, we may disclose or transfer information to a potential or actual third party purchaser of our business or assets.</p>
